la<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>PureGlow</title>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    background-color:#FFF8F5;
}

.header{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px 40px;
    background-color:#FFE4E1;
}

.header img{
    width:120px;
    height:80px;
    border-radius:10px;
}

.options{
    display:flex;
    gap:25px;
}

.options a{
    text-decoration:none;
    color:black;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.options a:hover{
    color:hotpink;
}

.btn{
    background-color:hotpink;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    border-radius:8px;
    padding:10px 20px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

.btn:hover{
    background-color:deeppink;
}

.home{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-around;
    align-items:center;
    padding:60px;
}

.homecontent{
    width:45%;
}

.homecontent h1{
    color:hotpink;
    font-size:40px;
}

.homecontent p{
    line-height:28px;
}

.homeimage img{
    width:350px;
    border-radius:15px;
}

.About{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-around;
    align-items:center;
    padding:60px;
    background-color:#FFF0F5;
}

.aboutcontent{
    width:50%;
}

.aboutcontent h1{
    color:hotpink;
    font-size:35px;
}

.aboutcontent p{
    line-height:28px;
}

.learnmore{
    color:purple;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.services{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:20px;
    padding:60px;
    background-color:#E8FFF4;
}

.servicescontent{
    grid-column:1/3;
    text-align:center;
}

.option1,
.option2{
    background-color:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-align:center;
}

.option1 h1,
.option2 h1{
    color:hotpink;
}

.option1:hover,
.option2:hover{
    background-color:hotpink;
}

.products{
    padding:60px;
}

.productitems{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.productitems h1{
    color:hotpink;
    font-size:35px;
}

.productlist{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap:20px;
}

.product1,
.product2,
.product3{
    background-color:pink;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-align:center;
}

.product1 img,
.product2 img,
.product3 img{
    width:150px;
    border-radius:10px;
}

.product1:hover,
.product2:hover,
.product3:hover{
    background-color:purple;
}

.Contact{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:20px;
    padding:60px;
    background-color:#FFE4E1;
}

.contactinfo{
    text-align:left;
}

.footercontent{
    background-color:hotpink;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-align:center;
}

.form{
    padding:50px;
}

form{
    width:350px;
    margin:auto;
}

form label{
    display:block;
    margin-top:10px;
    margin-bottom:5px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

form input{
    width:100%;
    padding:10px;
    border:1px solid gray;
    border-radius:5px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

form button{
    margin-top:10px;
}
</head>
</style>

<body>
    <section class="header">
        <h1>PURE GLOW</h1>
        <img src="images/pure glow.jpeg" alt="PureGlow Logo">

    <div class="options">
        <a href="">Home</a>
        <a href="">About</a>
        <a href="">Services</a>
        <a href="">Contact</a>
        <a href="">Products</a>
    </div>
 <button class="btn">more info  </button>
    </section>


    <section class="home">
        <div class="homecontent">
            <h1>Reveal your natural glow</h1>
            <p>Pure Glow helps you discover the perfect skincare routine using AI-powered recommendations. Get personalized advice based on your skin type and concerns</p>
            <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
        </div>

        
        <div class="homeimage">
            <img src="images/homeimage.png">
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="About">
        <div class="aboutcontent">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Pure Glow is a skincare brand dedicated to helping you achieve healthy, radiant skin. Our team of experts combines the latest scientific research with natural ingredients to create effective products that cater to your unique skin needs.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to make skincare simple, personalized, and effective through smart technology and trusted skincare guidance.</p>
            <button class="btn">Learn More</button>
        </div>
        
        

        <div class="learnmore">
            <p>Learn more about our story and values.</p>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="services">
            <div class="servicescontent">
                <h1>Our Services</h1>
                <p>We offer a range of services to help you achieve your skincare goals, including personalized skincare consultations, product recommendations, and access to our exclusive skincare community.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="option1">
                <h1>Product recommendation</h1>
                <p>Get personalized product recommendations based on your skin type and concerns.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="option2">
                    <h1>Skincare consultation</h1>
                    <p>Schedule a consultation with our skincare experts to receive tailored advice and guidance.</p>
                    </div>

                
                
            </div>
    </section>


    <section class="products">
        <div class="productitems">
            <h1>Featured Products</h1>
            <p>Explore our carefully selected skincare products designed to nourish and protect your skin every day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="productlist">
            <div class="product1">
                <img src="images/facialcleanser.png" alt="Facial Cleanser">
                <h2>Facial Cleanser</h2>
                <p>Gently cleanses and removes impurities for a fresh, radiant complexion.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="product2">
                <img src="images/nourishingmoisturizer.png" alt="Moisturizer">
                <h2>Moisturizer</h2>
                <p>Hydrates and nourishes the skin, leaving it soft and supple.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="product3">
                <img src="images/vitamincserum.png" alt="Vitamin C Serum">
                <h2>Vitamin C Serum</h2>
                <p>Boosts collagen production and brightens the skin for a more even complexion.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="Contact">
        <div class="contactinfo">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>Have questions or need assistance? Reach out to our support team, and we'll be happy to help you with your skincare journey.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="footercontent">
                <h1>PureGlow</h1>
                <p>Healthy skin,Happy life.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="form">
            <form action="">
                <label for="name">Your Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your Name"><br>

                <label for="email">Your Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Your Email">
                
                <button class="btn">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </section>

    </section>




</body>
</html>
